---
title: Roast Eggplant, Chicken & Cauliflower Couscous Bowl with Cucumber Salad & Garlic Yoghurt
description: This couscous bowl is packed to the brim with wholesome veggies, adding layers of flavour and texture to every mouthful. With a drizzle of garlikcy yoghurt and a sweet capsicum relish, this meal is a culinary delight that's good for the body and the soul!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

